{"tid":626323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國傳媒指英國核潛艇今晚發射巡航導彈攻擊敘利亞","createTime":"2018-04-12T04:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T04:05:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"89db2e7cdf9d54ba5add1a7b353e1344dad68386","tid":626323,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:27:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1002610&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1002610%26csid%3D261_367&d=Dt7%2BsZKySRTPXTrBALTzW6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=beb204b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1002610&amp;csid=261_367</a><br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒指英國核潛艇今晚發射巡航導彈攻擊敘利亞<br />\n<br />\n12.04.2018 11:42<br />\n<br />\n西方國家就敘利亞反對派受到化武襲擊、向敘利亞政府動武已如箭在弦。英國傳媒報導，英國皇家海軍一艘核動力攻擊型潛艇進入向敘利亞發射戰斧巡航導彈的位置，配合可以在當地時間今晚發動攻擊。而美國國防部長馬蒂斯表示，已經做好準備，為總統特朗普提供軍事選項。<br />\n<br />\n英國首相文翠珊早前說，英國參與這次對敘利亞的攻擊，事前無需國會的批准。"},{"pid":"76a1e1e5e940fbd18e651fce8d6c86db9cdeee36","tid":626323,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:30:46.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯話會攔截 兼 打翻導彈發射基地"},{"pid":"8d6a987eb5aef048e174d94af570a862ce860d36","tid":626323,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:34:57.000Z","msg":"打WW3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f760bb260343cc3e9e1e337f6f215fe265da9fbd","tid":626323,"uid":52215,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:36:10.000Z","msg":"俄佬夠唔夠單挑英美法一齊圍攻"},{"pid":"ee697bb10a38a457b1db9ebc2240c1f2692e84a0","tid":626323,"uid":23473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"情報控制邊可能咁廢..."},{"pid":"66a2728ebbe6414a3b248c8285b028d726f733b6","tid":626323,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76a1e1e5e940fbd18e651fce8d6c86db9cdeee36","tid":